Transient Experiences and Quantitative EEG Responses.” American Journal of
Clinical Hypnosis 41 (1999): 262–68.
Romach, M.K. et al. “Characteristics of Long-Term Alprazolam Users in the Community.”
Journal of Clinical Psychopharmacology 12 (1992): 316–21.
