Clonazepam, or No Benzodiazepine in Hospitalized Psychiatric Patients.”
Journal of Clinical Psychopharmacology 20 (2000): 7–11.
Rush, C.R., et al. “Abuse Liability of Alprazolam Relative to Other Commonly Used
