Review.” Journal of the American Medical Association 213 (1970): 996–1006.
Ng, B., and M. Alvear. “Dextropropoxyphene Addiction—A Drug of Primary Abuse.”
American Journal of Drug and Alcohol Abuse 19 (1993): 153–58.
